      LG21SchoolInformationSet.fromAccessAction_accessStatus_of_unobserved
        base test action
  · exact paper_theorem3_2_law_fairness_impossibility_of_certificate C

/--
Theorem 3.2 Section 3 continuous-law no-relevance form.
-/
